item.title: About Me
item.description: Cornell University Operations Research E-mail: jb2297 [@] cornell [DOT] edu I am an undergraduate student majoring in Operations Research and Information Engineering and minoring in Computer Science. I am involved with Prof.Udell’s research group, Cornell Data Science project team, Engineering Learning Initiative tutoring and Chorale. I am passionate about real life application of data science in a wide range of fields. Projects Population Segmentation For Health System Management The objective is to identify high resource use patients and to predict the length of stay and total cost of patients.
